👗 Wardrobe
Store looks in your virtual wardrobe. Personal shopping assistant helps you to find a new perfect outfit for your closet.
Follow your dress code, share your style with friends.
Create a personal lookbook like a stylist using seasonal colors.

🎨 Personal color palette
Use more than 100 colors from the seasonal color palette to create stylish, trendy & fashion looks.
Add favourite colors to the color palette using a color wheel.
Mix & match looks and accessories using an additional color palette with combined colors.

📷 Seasonal color analysis
Pass a simple seasonal color test based on four seasons color theory to know your color type (soft summer, warm autumn, deep winter, bright spring, etc.).
Use personal color analysis to enhance your natural beauty (skin tone, hair color, eye color).
Follow colors from a seasonal color palette that are in harmony with your features.

👚 Virtual fitting room
Use a virtual fitting room to try on outfits from online stores before the purchase.
Find an ideal look using a seasonal color palette. Select outfit according to your seasonal color type.
Try on a new outfit in 2 taps: take a selfie 👩, take a photo of your clothes.

Wardrobe:

👚

Dressing room:


☆ use a virtual fitting room to try on looks from online stores before the purchase;
☆ select an outfit according to your seasonal colors and make-up palette.

🎨

Personal color palettes:


☆ combine 120 colors from the seasonal color palettes to create stylish, trendy & fashion looks;
☆ add favorite colors to the color palette using a color wheel;
☆ mix and match looks and accessories using an additional color palette with color combinations.

💄

Make-up palettes:


☆ explore 70 make-up colors for each color type (lipsticks, eyeshadows, eyeliners, blushes);
☆ apply virtual makeover to see the entire look.
